          "instruction": "Apply trapezium area formula",
          "working": "Area = ½ × (12 + 8) × 6 = ½ × 20 × 6",
          "result": "= 60 cm²",
          "voice_text": "Area equals half times sum of parallel sides times height. Half of 20 times 6 equals 60."
        }
      ],
      "trick_id": null,
