      "difficulty": "hard",
      "marks": 4,
      "question_text": "A field is in the shape of a polygon ABCDE. The diagonal from A is 20 m. Perpendiculars from B, C, D, E to the diagonal are 5 m, 8 m, 6 m and 4 m respectively on alternating sides. Find the area of the field.",
